arch lesser_dwarven_guard
name Fwermir the Dwarven Guard
msg
@match hi|hello
Hello sonny.
I happen to work for the dwarven
military. It's a very boring job. All I
do is wait to be attacked,wait for
dragons,or stop robbers. I never have a
real adventure. So I come here to
gossip about my old adventures.
@match old adventures
Aye,I have had many adventures. Once
when i had only a scruff of a
beard,I lay hiding twenty,no ten paces
I say,away from one of the great
dragon lords. He was terrible to
behold,his great stature twelve feet
tall,magnificent wings upon his
back,red scales glistening in the
sunlight,claws and teeth like spears
and swords,his breath uttered forth
great flames. And even tho I am known
for stoutness of heart and great
courage,I cowered in the ditch till
the wyrm lord left.



endmsg
